    <item>
      <title>房地产公司 Adler 希望以高达 47% 的折扣出售资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/property-firm-adler-looks-to-sell-assets-at-up-to-47-discount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的德国房东阿德勒集团 (Adler Group SA) 已请求其债券持有人允许以较 2022 年估值折让 47% 的价格出售一处未完工的公寓开发项目，因为该公司正在竞相偿还巨额债务负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/property-firm-adler-looks-to-sell-assets-at-up-to-47-discount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
